{"tid":1623940,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"真心唔建議臨時政府，對依家個運動好不利 依一刻","createTime":"2019-10-05T02:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:46:46.000Z","uid":222970,"like":23,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"17e8f983ddacb94d272161d4ff82e9b4c200cb76","tid":1623940,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:23:26.000Z","msg":"我地依家又冇自己既特首 軍隊 <br />\n<br />\n連警察都未鬥得贏 得果幾個磚頭 <br />\n<br />\n成立臨時政府？會唔會ff得太多？連美國都唔支持<br />\n<br />\n暫時唔建議提及 臨時政府 港獨，自治比較好<br />\n<br />\n其實自己宣稱向外公佈 香港人可以講一套做一套<br />\n<br />\n你向外宣稱 只想一國兩制同自治 但可以心想獨立並低調做籌備工作<br />\n<br />\n我地依家毫無籌碼，處於下風唔建議直接攤牌"},{"pid":"8e60ab7049319f6393e1f279de0c70040608d5c7","tid":1623940,"uid":222970,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:25:35.000Z","msg":"跟住G phone既方向去做啦<br />\n<br />\nG phone就識玩啦 仲承認香港係中國<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢唔想承認 但時勢同形勢要佢承認"},{"pid":"128bdfa55a9fbcf2bd08db31f1504207ab6d004b","tid":1623940,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:28:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">10月5全城休息一日</span></span>"},{"pid":"ee0802696194679b1367fdb035d88cdb029df755","tid":1623940,"uid":222970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:35:41.000Z","msg":"我都好想獨立 臨時政府 但呢一刻搞真係對我地不利<br />\n<br />\n暫時黎講 唔建議做一d 對人權法案會影響既野"},{"pid":"20d539c0c21df218a35441ad7a1da8a27d28022c","tid":1623940,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:44:29.000Z","msg":"歷代各地成立臨時政府之前 必先掌控武裝力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請各位參考歷史，唔好比盲目衝昏頭腦<br />\n<br />\n我地係要實際勝利，而唔係幻想既勝利<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/臨時政府\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFgxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=1fbaf345\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/臨時政府</a>"},{"